sentences.sentence: The “overwhelming cultural attitude” militates against it, Mr. Holmes said.
sentences.translation: 霍姆斯说，“压倒一切的文化态度妨碍了这种措施的实施。”

sentences.sentence: Expect no pressure from fellow asians-regional custom militates against telling tyrants that they stink.
sentences.translation: 其它的亚洲国家不会给他任何压力。地区习惯使得没有人告诉暴君，他们很讨厌。
